So the date was what i would call a success. its funny though how you hang out with someone all the time and you are perfectly find and no nerves. then when you get in a situation..a romantic situation i suppose, you go this totally different person. Tim and I we talk all the time just about random shit. but last night it was like we had nothing to talk about. but we managed. sad thing his pay didn't go through so i had to pay for like the majority of the dinner. which didn't bother me. i don't get why the guy has to pay anyway. it is so double standard...oooh shit wait gotta find the puppy.

ok found it. bloody thing gets into everything. now where was i...ah yes dinner. anyway. we finished up OH and by the way my food was DISGUSTING...i don't eat seafood and where we went the food is like basically all seafood. well. i had chicken and pear salad. it was gross. i only ate the little chicken pieces out of it and then they were really that nice anyway!! haha. but ohwell. i ate when i got home!! so we finished up and he drove me home. walked me to the door and kissed. i wanted to laugh i don't know why!!! anyway went inside and about 10 seconds after he rings...can i come inside now? bahaha. i was in hysterics!!!! so he came in and we watched movies.

So today i have to go and bloody time netball. in like 2 hours. i don't want to but hey i got a bottle of midori out of it so im happy :)

so yeah that was the date. he will be drunk tonight and ill get to laugh at him!! teehee

OH and ASH i've missed your ass!! xxx

love brittah <3

So tonight is a first date for my boyfriend and i. yes he already is my boyfriend but that doesn't matter. we have never been on a first date, when we first started seeing each other we would just meet up when we were drunk and hook up. it was fun. then we started hanging out more then became a couple. so this is our first offical date and to tell you the truth im a little nervous!!!

im not entirely sure why im so nervous. we always have something to talk about and we get along great. im just scared we are gonna sit there and go all silent because we have talked about everything. maybe i should get drunk before i go? No no i won't do that.....haha..but the next big question is WHAT TO WEAR!! ahhh i need a stylist to choose my clothes. i think it may just wear jeans and a top. don't wanna be too dressy. its just a casual dinner right? yeah. it is.

So i went for a surf this morning to clear my mind. it was refreshing yet cold. OHHH and i got a job at woolies..i know woolies right not much of a career. but im gonna do other stuff also. i don't wanna stay there forever and be a check out chick. not what i want to do with my life. but it's a job and it's money so im happy with that. i need money haha. i have been doing some work at the footy club but that gets boring. everyone just gets drunk. im not working this weekend though so i might have a couple of drinks and i know that if the boys win they will get in to the grandy and it will be a big one. i hope they win!! they i can get drunk at the grandy!!! i just fucken hope i dont have to work...then i will be PISSED off. and i hope i don't have to work state titles weekend!! hahahaaha.

anyway should go and do some ironing or otherwise ill have to wear creased clothes!! haha wish me luck tonight..

<3 britt

Wow. Keely just showed me this video about a little girl who died from child abuse. i cant understand why they would give her back to her mother knowing that she was getting abused. the saddest thing is that it still happens today. its heart wrenching how could someone harm a small child or any child for that matter. people are sick and it is disgusting that their are people out there that do that.

Well this is it. first post for a very very long time. haha keely made me!! and she made this awesome layout for me..i just gotta put the mood theme up then im all done..

so stay tuned for my new life

Today my life sucked. Totally. And it started after lunch. I had lunch at home as i always do and Ben was here with Bradyn coz they had the day off. Both on the same day. Please tell me that wasn't half planned? Anyway i asked Ben if i could take his car back to work as mine didn't have that much petrol. After a big sigh and a roll of the eyes, he finally gave me his keys and i asked him if he could please fill mine up for me...he replied with ' anything else princess?' i just shook my head and left. 

Work sucked customers kept abusing me for things i had no idea about. Fuck. Don't shoot the messenger. Then i get home ( oh and i'm sick coz Ben doesn't go to the doctor and get antibiotics ) and find out that i need to be at netball training at like 6:15pm i finish work at 5:30pm takes 15 minutes to drive home. I get home and go and get changed and Ben decides he wants to go out for dinner. I said i couldn't coz i have netball and he knew that. Whatever he cracks it and says i never spend anytime with him blah blah. And i said he may as well go out with Bradyn coz he does everything with him. I didn't say anymore and left ot go to Deanna's so we could go to netball. 

Well netball was shit. I fell over.. and it's raining and i grazed my elbow and hurt my wrist. It hurts. I get home i'm hungry, cold, in pain and i wanna die. So i get dinner and then pour myself a drink and i spill it, because well my wrist hurts. Then well i cried coz i was in pain and NO ONE CARED. Ben walked out and looked at the mess on the floor and said...and i quote ' There's No Use Crying Over Spilt Milk'I looked at him and said ' It isn't Milk you wanker' and i left my dinner and went to watch Prision Break. Which he didn't want to watch so he sat there and sulked.

He is in bed now thank fuck for that. Sick of him and the world today kinda wanna DIE. My arm hurts...my throat is pissing me off and my nose will not stop running...i get too hot in bed coz of my electric blanket. John and Ash got voted off of big brother and Ben didn't tape it for me tonight. I haven't eaten and i spilt my drink. I'm coughing and it hurts. I don't get to talk to Chris or Tash anymore coz we are never on at the same time. Tegan's post made me sad, because of the things that happened. Did i mention my arm hurts. ......

I can whinge here right? Too Bad. Bed. <3 Britt

Wow. I haven't done a proper post in here for like ages. So much has happened in that time. But i'm not going to go back and recap every passing minute of my life. No point living in the past right? No. Move on forward..

So. I now have myself a great boyfriend. His name is Ben and he is so awesome. Really he is. At first we didn't think anything was going t happen coz he is good friends with my brother, and well Bradyn is a pain in the ass and was telling us we couldn't get together coz it would be wrong. But we told him to just chill and it will be all cool and now well he loves it coz ' we all get to hang together'. haha. What a loser.

So i was supposed to go out this weekend but i didn't. Ben had been away for the week working and he came back early to suprise me and i just didn't want to go out. Even though it's the long weekend here and all, i should have been out getting trashed but it just didn't do it for me. I do that every weekend. My friend Ash hates it when i get a boyfriend, she says i don't do anything and i don't go out i just stay at home and watch movies with my man. So what if i do? Why do i have to go out everyweekend. Oh get this conversation i had with my friend:

Nadia: So you coming out tonight or what?
Me: Nope. Why?
Nadia: Coz i think that it is necessary that you do.
Me: Why?
Nadia: You come out and i'll tell you why
Me: I'm not going anywhere. I'm staying home for the whole weekend. Go out with your other friends.
Nadia: You have no choice in the matter Britt, your coming out. So go and get dressed
Me: -Laughs- i have choice and i'm not going out. I don't want to go out. I'm over going out. You only want me to go out so when you get your arse kicked by your ex boyfriends new girlfriend i can back you up
Nadia: No that is not why. I think you need to come out. Ben isn't back yet, come out and have fun before you go under the thumb.
Me: Nadia don't you have anyone to go out with?
Nadia: Yeah, Karly is coming. 
Me: Well, go out with Karly. Because Ben is back and i'm not going out. Conversation over.
Nadia: Well come and have a few drinks with us then, see how you feel.
Me: Ohh i see how it is. You want me to come and hang so when you guys are ready to go out i can drop you there. 
Nadia: Oh My God Britt. get a grip we want you to come out and have fun, not use you.
Me: your so full of shit. Go away.
-Britt leaves-

Yeh my friends can't take no for an answer. Anyway Nadia rings me at like 4:30am saying she needs to ask me a question. I didn't answer my phone, it went to voice message. Like i'm gonna have my phone on when i know they are out. I've learnt my lesson. Well Bradyn went out and he came home and was like 'Guess Who Was All Over Me?' and Ben and i were watching a movie and Ben was like ' Ya Nanna?' and Bradyn was like 'Close. Nadia' i nearly spat my food out. She wanted ME to go out because she wanted BRADYN to go out also. Stupid cow could've just asked if he was going out. SHE was using me.....to get to my brother. Good luck to her i say.....

Anyway i will try and keep this updated more. I promise. So peach out people

<3 Brittani

[Ex Boyfriends Suck]

I'm confused. You break up with someone and they are in the past. Yet for some reason you still have feelings for them and even when you have moved on they still make you feel guilty for moving on and not having feelings for them anymore. Especially when they break it off with you. They move on, you still sit around thinking about them and the what if's but when you finally decide that there is no use wasting your life thinking about them, they turn around and say they still love you? What are you supposed to do? Lie and say i love you too lets try it again blah blah. That would be fine if the break up was a good break up, but then again when is a break up a good one. 

My Ex is a total ass. TOTAL ass. I sat around crying over him because he broke up with me because he had feelings for another girl. He didn't cheat on me, he broke up with me too see how much he liked her and he liked her alot. I was heart broken. We were ENGAGED for god sake. You don't say 'Will You Marry Me' and then like a month later reveal your in love with someone else. Well anyway that was like 6 months ago right. And he starts calling me again. He tells me that iam still his girl and i can't go out anymore unless he says i can and if he hears about me being with another guy he will kill them.
